TCL Communication has launched the MoveTime Family Watch (MT30) in South Africa. The watch is based on Qualcomm’s Snapdragon Wear 2100 platform and is aimed at helping parents stay connected with their children. It features calling and messaging functionality, location tracking, geofencing alerts, and an SOS button that calls for help in an emergency. The MT30 also offers up to two days of battery life, is water resistant up to 1m in static water, and is IP67 dust-proof. The MT30 is available through Vodacom for R2,699, or on contract for R149 per month on a uChoose Flexi 110.